---
import CTA from "../components/CTA.astro";
import Hero from "../components/Hero.astro";
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="For Engineering Leaders - Meshum" description="Stop losing productivity to knowledge fragmentation. Meshum helps engineering teams move faster by making every answer instant and every decision traceable.">
	<!-- Hero section with metrics -->
	<Hero
		label="For Engineering Leaders"
		heading="Your engineers spend"
		gradientText="10 hours a week searching."
		subheading="That's 25% of your engineering budget spent hunting for answers that already exist. Meshum gives those hours back—so your team ships faster, onboards in days not months, and scales without chaos."
		variant="full-screen"
		maxWidth="6xl"
	>
		<!-- Key metrics -->
		<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
			<div class="p-6 rounded-xl bg-surface/80 backdrop-blur border border-border">
				<div class="text-4xl font-heading font-bold text-benefit-1 mb-2">2.4hrs</div>
				<div class="text-sm font-body text-muted">saved per engineer daily</div>
			</div>
			<div class="p-6 rounded-xl bg-surface/80 backdrop-blur border border-border">
				<div class="text-4xl font-heading font-bold text-benefit-2 mb-2">40%</div>
				<div class="text-sm font-body text-muted">faster onboarding time</div>
			</div>
			<div class="p-6 rounded-xl bg-surface/80 backdrop-blur border border-border">
				<div class="text-4xl font-heading font-bold text-benefit-3 mb-2">95%</div>
				<div class="text-sm font-body text-muted">reduction in repeat questions</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</Hero>

	<!-- The Business Case -->
	<section class="py-32 bg-page">
		<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
			<div class="text-center mb-16">
				<div class="inline-block mb-6">
					<span class="px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-primary/10 border border-primary/20 text-primary text-sm font-medium">
						The Cost of Fragmented Knowledge
					</span>
				</div>
				<h2 class="font-heading text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-foreground mb-6">
					every interrupt costs money
				</h2>
				<p class="font-body text-xl text-muted max-w-3xl mx-auto">
					When knowledge lives in a dozen different tools, your team pays in wasted hours, missed deadlines, and burned budget.
				</p>
			</div>

			<!-- Problem breakdown -->
			<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6 mb-16">
				<div class="p-6 rounded-xl bg-surface border border-border">
					<div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-red-500/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
						<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-red-600 dark:text-red-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
						</svg>
					</div>
					<h3 class="font-heading text-lg font-bold text-foreground mb-2">Lost Productivity</h3>
					<p class="font-body text-sm text-muted mb-3">Engineers spend 10 hours/week hunting for answers across Slack, GitHub, Confluence, and Notion. That's a quarter of their work week.</p>
					<p class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold text-red-600 dark:text-red-400">$60K/year</p>
					<p class="font-body text-xs text-muted">wasted per senior engineer</p>
				</div>

				<div class="p-6 rounded-xl bg-surface border border-border">
					<div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-orange-500/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
						<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-orange-600 dark:text-orange-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 7V3m8 4V3m-9 8h10M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z"/>
						</svg>
					</div>
					<h3 class="font-heading text-lg font-bold text-foreground mb-2">Slow Onboarding</h3>
					<p class="font-body text-sm text-muted mb-3">New hires take 3-6 months to become productive because critical knowledge lives in people's heads, not in searchable systems.</p>
					<p class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold text-orange-600 dark:text-orange-400">6 weeks</p>
					<p class="font-body text-xs text-muted">before first real contribution</p>
				</div>

				<div class="p-6 rounded-xl bg-surface border border-border">
					<div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-yellow-500/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
						<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-yellow-600 dark:text-yellow-500" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01m-6.938 4h13.856c1.54 0 2.502-1.667 1.732-3L13.732 4c-.77-1.333-2.694-1.333-3.464 0L3.34 16c-.77 1.333.192 3 1.732 3z"/>
						</svg>
					</div>
					<h3 class="font-heading text-lg font-bold text-foreground mb-2">Knowledge Silos</h3>
					<p class="font-body text-sm text-muted mb-3">"Only Sarah knows that" creates bottlenecks. Projects stall when key people are out. Critical context disappears when people leave.</p>
					<p class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold text-yellow-600 dark:text-yellow-500">High risk</p>
					<p class="font-body text-xs text-muted">of project delays</p>
				</div>

				<div class="p-6 rounded-xl bg-surface border border-border">
					<div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-red-500/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
						<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-red-600 dark:text-red-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 17h8m0 0V9m0 8l-8-8-4 4-6-6"/>
						</svg>
					</div>
					<h3 class="font-heading text-lg font-bold text-foreground mb-2">Context Switching</h3>
					<p class="font-body text-sm text-muted mb-3">Your senior engineers spend their day answering the same questions over Slack instead of building. Every interrupt breaks flow.</p>
					<p class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold text-red-600 dark:text-red-400">4 hours/day</p>
					<p class="font-body text-xs text-muted">lost to interruptions</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<!-- ROI Calculator -->
			<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto p-8 rounded-2xl bg-linear-to-br from-solution-bg-start to-solution-bg-end border border-solution-accent/20 shadow-xl">
				<h3 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold text-foreground mb-6 text-center">Calculate your savings</h3>

				<div class="space-y-4">
					<div class="flex items-center justify-between p-4 rounded-lg bg-white/70 dark:bg-elevated/70 backdrop-blur">
						<div>
							<div class="font-heading font-semibold text-foreground">Team size</div>
							<div class="text-sm text-muted">Number of engineers</div>
						</div>
						<div class="font-heading text-3xl font-bold text-primary">20</div>
					</div>

					<div class="flex items-center justify-between p-4 rounded-lg bg-white/70 dark:bg-elevated/70 backdrop-blur">
						<div>
							<div class="font-heading font-semibold text-foreground">Time saved per engineer</div>
							<div class="text-sm text-muted">Hours per week</div>
						</div>
						<div class="font-heading text-3xl font-bold text-accent">10</div>
					</div>

					<div class="h-px bg-border my-4"></div>

					<div class="p-6 rounded-lg bg-linear-to-br from-primary to-accent text-white">
						<div class="text-center">
							<div class="text-sm font-body mb-2">Annual productivity recovered</div>
							<div class="font-heading text-5xl font-bold mb-2">$1.2M</div>
							<div class="text-sm font-body opacity-90">= 10,400 engineering hours/year</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<p class="text-xs text-muted text-center mt-6 italic">
					Based on $120K average fully-loaded engineer cost
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- The Solution: What Meshum Does -->
	<section class="py-32 bg-surface">
		<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
			<div class="text-center mb-16">
				<div class="inline-block mb-6">
					<span class="px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-solution-accent/10 border border-solution-accent/20 text-solution-accent text-sm font-medium">
						The Meshum Solution
					</span>
				</div>
				<h2 class="font-heading text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-foreground mb-6">
					one unified knowledge layer.
					<br>
					zero wasted hours.
				</h2>
				<p class="font-body text-xl text-muted max-w-3xl mx-auto">
					Meshum connects your team's scattered knowledge—code, docs, conversations, decisions—into one searchable system. Every answer instant. Every answer cited.
				</p>
			</div>

			<!-- Benefits for leaders -->
			<div class="grid lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
				<!-- Benefit 1 -->
				<div class="p-8 rounded-2xl bg-page border border-border hover:shadow-xl transition-all">
					<div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-xl bg-linear-to-br from-benefit-1 to-benefit-1/60 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 shadow-lg">
						<svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7h8m0 0v8m0-8l-8 8-4-4-6 6"/>
						</svg>
					</div>
					<h3 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold text-foreground mb-4">Ship 40% faster</h3>
					<p class="font-body text-muted leading-relaxed mb-4">
						Your team stops waiting for answers. Features ship faster when every engineer has instant access to context—not buried in someone's head or lost in Slack.
					</p>
					<ul class="space-y-2">
						<li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm font-body text-muted">
							<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-benefit-1 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
								<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
							</svg>
							<span>Work doesn't stop when people take PTO</span>
						</li>
						<li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm font-body text-muted">
							<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-benefit-1 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
								<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
							</svg>
							<span>No more handoff delays between teams</span>
						</li>
						<li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm font-body text-muted">
							<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-benefit-1 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
								<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
							</svg>
							<span>Sprint blockers drop by 60%</span>
						</li>
					</ul>
				</div>

				<!-- Benefit 2 -->
				<div class="p-8 rounded-2xl bg-page border border-border hover:shadow-xl transition-all">
					<div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-xl bg-linear-to-br from-benefit-2 to-benefit-2/60 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 shadow-lg">
						<svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 4.354a4 4 0 110 5.292M15 21H3v-1a6 6 0 0112 0v1zm0 0h6v-1a6 6 0 00-9-5.197M13 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0z"/>
						</svg>
					</div>
					<h3 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold text-foreground mb-4">Onboard in days, not months</h3>
					<p class="font-body text-muted leading-relaxed mb-4">
						New hires get instant access to years of decisions, context, and tribal knowledge. They ship code in week 1, not week 6—without burning your senior engineers' time.
					</p>
					<ul class="space-y-2">
						<li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm font-body text-muted">
							<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-benefit-2 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
								<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
							</svg>
							<span>Find answers without bothering teammates</span>
						</li>
						<li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm font-body text-muted">
							<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-benefit-2 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
								<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
							</svg>
							<span>Ship first feature in week 1, not month 2</span>
						</li>
						<li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm font-body text-muted">
							<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-benefit-2 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
								<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
							</svg>
							<span>Cut onboarding costs in half</span>
						</li>
					</ul>
				</div>

				<!-- Benefit 3 -->
				<div class="p-8 rounded-2xl bg-page border border-border hover:shadow-xl transition-all">
					<div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-xl bg-linear-to-br from-benefit-3 to-benefit-3/60 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 shadow-lg">
						<svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"/>
						</svg>
					</div>
					<h3 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold text-foreground mb-4">Scale without chaos</h3>
					<p class="font-body text-muted leading-relaxed mb-4">
						Growing from 10 to 100 engineers usually means exponential communication overhead. Meshum keeps institutional knowledge accessible and searchable at any size.
					</p>
					<ul class="space-y-2">
						<li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm font-body text-muted">
							<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-benefit-3 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
								<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
							</svg>
							<span>Break down knowledge silos automatically</span>
						</li>
						<li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm font-body text-muted">
							<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-benefit-3 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
								<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
							</svg>
							<span>Context survives when people leave</span>
						</li>
						<li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm font-body text-muted">
							<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-benefit-3 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
								<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
							</svg>
							<span>Reduce single points of failure</span>
						</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Social Proof / Use Cases -->
	<section class="py-32 bg-page">
		<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
			<div class="text-center mb-16">
				<h2 class="font-heading text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-foreground mb-6">
					Built for modern engineering teams
				</h2>
			</div>

			<div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
				<!-- Use case 1 -->
				<div class="p-8 rounded-2xl bg-surface border border-border">
					<div class="mb-4">
						<div class="inline-block px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-primary/10 border border-primary/20 text-primary text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider">
							Fast-growing Startups
						</div>
					</div>
					<h3 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-foreground mb-3">
						scaling from 5 to 40 engineers
					</h3>
					<p class="font-body text-muted leading-relaxed">
						When you're doubling headcount every six months, institutional knowledge usually gets lost. Meshum captures context automatically so new hires ramp without monopolizing your senior engineers.
					</p>
				</div>

				<!-- Use case 2 -->
				<div class="p-8 rounded-2xl bg-surface border border-border">
					<div class="mb-4">
						<div class="inline-block px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-accent/10 border border-accent/20 text-accent text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider">
							Remote-first Teams
						</div>
					</div>
					<h3 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-foreground mb-3">
						no more waiting across timezones
					</h3>
					<p class="font-body text-muted leading-relaxed">
						Distributed teams usually lose 8+ hours waiting for the person who knows to wake up. Meshum makes every engineer self-sufficient at 3am or 3pm.
					</p>
				</div>

				<!-- Use case 3 -->
				<div class="p-8 rounded-2xl bg-surface border border-border">
					<div class="mb-4">
						<div class="inline-block px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-benefit-3/10 border border-benefit-3/20 text-benefit-3 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider">
							Enterprise Teams
						</div>
					</div>
					<h3 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-foreground mb-3">
						decades of context, one search
					</h3>
					<p class="font-body text-muted leading-relaxed">
						Large codebases and legacy systems create mountains of tribal knowledge. Meshum captures it all so your team stops asking the same questions year after year.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Implementation: No disruption -->
	<section class="py-32 bg-linear-to-br from-solution-bg-start to-solution-bg-end">
		<div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
			<div class="text-center mb-16">
				<div class="inline-block mb-6">
					<span class="px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-solution-accent/10 border border-solution-accent/20 text-solution-accent text-sm font-medium">
						Zero Disruption
					</span>
				</div>
				<h2 class="font-heading text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-foreground mb-6">
					live in 5 minutes.
					<br>
					ROI in the first week.
				</h2>
			</div>

			<!-- Timeline -->
			<div class="relative">
				<!-- Vertical line -->
				<div class="absolute left-8 top-0 bottom-0 w-0.5 bg-border"></div>

				<div class="space-y-8">
					<!-- Step 1 -->
					<div class="flex items-start gap-6">
						<div class="shrink-0 w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-linear-to-br from-primary to-primary/60 flex items-center justify-center text-white font-heading font-bold text-xl shadow-lg relative z-10">
							1
						</div>
						<div class="flex-1 pt-3">
							<h3 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-foreground mb-2">Connect your tools</h3>
							<p class="font-body text-muted">One-click OAuth for GitHub, Slack, Confluence, Notion. No migration required. No data export. Just authorize and you're done.</p>
						</div>
					</div>

					<!-- Step 2 -->
					<div class="flex items-start gap-6">
						<div class="shrink-0 w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-linear-to-br from-accent to-accent/60 flex items-center justify-center text-white font-heading font-bold text-xl shadow-lg relative z-10">
							2
						</div>
						<div class="flex-1 pt-3">
							<h3 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-foreground mb-2">Meshum indexes everything</h3>
							<p class="font-body text-muted">The AI processes your code, docs, and conversations to build a searchable knowledge graph. Takes about 10 minutes for most teams.</p>
						</div>
					</div>

					<!-- Step 3 -->
					<div class="flex items-start gap-6">
						<div class="shrink-0 w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-linear-to-br from-benefit-3 to-benefit-3/60 flex items-center justify-center text-white font-heading font-bold text-xl shadow-lg relative z-10">
							3
						</div>
						<div class="flex-1 pt-3">
							<h3 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-foreground mb-2">Your team starts asking</h3>
							<p class="font-body text-muted">Zero training required. Engineers ask questions in plain English and get answers with source citations. That's it.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="mt-16 p-8 rounded-2xl bg-white/70 dark:bg-elevated/70 backdrop-blur border border-border text-center">
				<p class="font-body text-lg text-foreground mb-4">
					<span class="font-bold">Your data stays in your infrastructure.</span> We never train models on your knowledge. Full control over access and permissions.
				</p>
				<p class="font-body text-sm text-muted">
					Enterprise SSO • Role-based access • Audit logs • Self-hosted options available
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Call to action section -->
	<CTA
		heading="see the ROI in week one"
		subheading="Book a demo to see how Meshum recovers 10 hours per engineer, every week."
		buttonText="Book a Demo"
		footerText="5-minute setup • 30-day money-back guarantee • Enterprise-ready"
		maxWidth="4xl"
	/>
</Layout>

<style>
	/* Subtle animated gradient */
	@keyframes gradient {
		0%, 100% {
			opacity: 0.3;
		}
		50% {
			opacity: 0.5;
		}
	}

	.animate-gradient {
		animation: gradient 8s ease-in-out infinite;
	}

	/* Gradient text animation */
	@keyframes gradient-text {
		0%, 100% {
			background-position: 0 50%;
		}
		50% {
			background-position: 100% 50%;
		}
	}

	.animate-gradient-text {
		background-size: 200% 200%;
		animation: gradient-text 6s ease-in-out infinite;
	}

	/* Fade in animation */
	@keyframes fadeIn {
		from {
			opacity: 0;
			transform: translateY(20px);
		}
		to {
			opacity: 1;
			transform: translateY(0);
		}
	}

	.fade-in {
		opacity: 0;
		animation: fadeIn 0.8s ease-out forwards;
	}

	/* Smooth font rendering */
	* {
		-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
		-moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale;
	}
</style>
